Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小遥  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呦  吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是为了封锁线路所以把树放倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你好歹也说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从碓冰第三桥梁到横川间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该正在为碓冰齿轨线通车进行维护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不会有什么危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坡度又开始陡起来了  速度也下不来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井  岩泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了\N交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这搞不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隧道太狭小了  要怎么办  高山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:04:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是在隧道里有墙顶着  不会进一步倾斜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代理班长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要脱开墙壁就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了  代理班长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说别在高速行驶的车辆上瞎搞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  多亏你了  不过别再这么干了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解  代理班长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是旧线最长的第六隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙啊  得想想怎么把速度再降下来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩泉君  用全力踩踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？  这么做不是会加速吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为换到了齿轨档  所以现在只会转动地板下面的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动力不会被传导到车轮的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  齿轨驱动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信越本线直到1963年都配备有登山铁路使用的齿轨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条旧线也留下了这些齿轨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要让车下的齿轮和齿轨顺利啮合的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  说不定可以顺利通过曲线而不脱轨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:06:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会有冲击  大家抓好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我咬上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃啊  不是说要做列车司机的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山君  再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再踩快点  岩泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬合上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:07:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但以这种速度冲下去的话  就真要翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,齿轨啮合上的话应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我转过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  作战很成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不用踩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩泉  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踢墙壁的时候稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了  你先休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到碓冰第三桥梁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是在空中跑一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊人的高度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要进第五隧道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么干对齿轨装置绝对是个不小的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能撑到横川吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高  高山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意点啊  樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是最后一个隧道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的隧道都通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,齿轨装置坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要坏得再早点就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里下去就和新线的下行线汇合了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好接下来只剩横川前面的S弯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山你说的轻松  我差点因为你的驾驶把命给丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  不过也算是顺利过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这前面真的没关系吗  刚才连零件都掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然齿轨装置坏了  但接下来的斜坡都不算陡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有D设备的发电制动就没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是承受不住超出预想的负荷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来只能靠这个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有连续使用制动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该没有坏才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:11:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可感觉没有之前那么有效了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是产生了弱化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦连续使用制动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制动盘就会变热随之加热闸瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变热的闸瓦会使闸管内产生气体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而妨碍制动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要闲置不用一段时间应该就会冷却恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在到站的时候  制动是必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望在这之前都不去用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曲线还剩几个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个  马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩泉  你代我来驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就操作这一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入车站后  使劲把制动杆扳下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算只靠移动重心拐过这两个弯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我也来做  拜托和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山  这能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象的要恐怖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也不想做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是除此之外没有其他办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曲线还有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是丸山曲线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不集中精神的话  会掉下去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道这种时候该怎么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把想说的话大声喊出来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要成为列车司机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就高山来说  这次意外很努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然下一个就是最后了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是是个非常严峻的曲线
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们进入横川与轻井泽之间最长的直线区间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸山直线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  虽说比较平缓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因为有坡度  速度会变快的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就是最后的曲线了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井  要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解  代理班长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好强的离心力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点事  我也能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是横川站哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是红灯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄色是场内注意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是可以进入车站的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  岩泉  制动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太用力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后的手段了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩泉制动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太强了  岩泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  制动再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有跳下去了  小遥你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山  小遥就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海  要跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周转箱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是日本器官机构的大糸小姐所托管的器官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我们先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  高山君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你陪我任性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前  一个很重要的人因为同样的情况去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能忍受这样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你准备抱到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就只是高山  自我感觉太良好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算任务完成了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很狼狈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  都是因为我不够强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终归就是只有这点程度的代理班长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  开始加入国铁时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想当的不是铁道公安队员而是列车司机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  现在的我是铁道公安队员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些都是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:19:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  今后能和我一起在警四工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  代理班长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后也请多关照哦  代理班长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练结束  训练结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急行「白山」  轻井泽至横川间连接正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车内无较大冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接部无损害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  突然腰板就挺直了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸节奏也很一致
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休假期间发生了什么好的事情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  不是  没什么特别
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我信奉的主义是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你们是打架了还是亲在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:20:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要结果是好的  我都没意见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  没有啦  那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这次算你勉强及格了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但作为列车司机  你还嫩的很
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  以后还要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候我会好好锻炼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实习结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  首先去吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没吃饱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不快点的话乃亚的表演就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会被骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札沼好厉害啊  无论和谁都能相处得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我和乃亚是对手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么方面的对手啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  听说国铁对你们的衣服进行了赔偿？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要买一件比较容易行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种果然还是不适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  我倒觉得很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽  虽然就那么一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是既然高山你这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再找找看的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来看看这个  好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山  我要去铁道公安队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去驾驶课
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好保护高山驾驶的列车的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就必须圆满完成这次OJT  两个人都顺利进入国铁才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定高山不行啊  就那样的驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢  那次是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多意外事件而且我也没拿出真本事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着餐车、休闲车和包厢车
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为日本第一列豪华寝台特急的北斗星号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是来往于上野与札幌之间无需换乘的寝台特急列车
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走行里程达1215千米
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.38,0:23:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  这里本应该是直人来解说的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.40,0:24:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  怎么这么严肃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我一个人做了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.55,0:24:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RAIL WARS!  第十话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.56,0:24:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我保密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.35,0:24:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这么说定了  直人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:38.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}注：参考德国哈茨山铁路采用的齿轨铁道，当时工程师仙石贡和吉川三次郎\N决定采用齿轨铁道翻越碓冰岭。因折返式线路受制于编组长度且需停车折返\N浪费时间，而修建迂回展线使搬运物资十分困难、造价高昂且速度相比直接\N爬坡相差无几，故采用沿旧国道18号修建最大坡度66.7‰的齿轨线路翻越碓\N冰岭，即利于物资搬运也节约成本并可实现通行效率最大化。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}二战后日本铁道输送量激增，横轻旧线已经无法满足行车需求，修建新线的\N计划从而浮出水面。曾有方案提出修建最大坡度22.5‰的迂回展线，但随着\N技术进步，当时条件下可以实现普通粘着铁道爬上66.7‰的陡坡，为了保证\N输送效率，新线继续采用旧线的路径并在旧线旁边建设，1963年新线开通。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}注：碓冰第三桥梁全长91米，距河底高度31米，使用红砖200万余块建造，\N是日本现存使用红砖最多的桥梁。于1882年由英国工程师帕伍那沃和日本\N工程师古川晴一共同设计。1993年连同周边4座桥梁作为「碓冰铁道设施」\N被列入日本国家重要文化财产。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.70,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}注：日本现代的铁道信号为速度制信号，其中车内信号式是纯速度制信号\N方式，地面信号式为速度制与选路制相结合以速度制为核心的信号方式。\N一个黄灯亮起是注意信号，限速45km/h（不同公司略与区别），下一信号\N机可能是警戒或停止信号。场内注意代表场内信号机（类似于中国的进站\N信号机但有不同）为注意信号，指示列车进站停车。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.50,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}与中国不同的是，日本的场内信号机是可以设置多个的，也就是说车站内\N的到发线可以分成多段、咽喉可以分成若干个区域，将站内划分出多个闭\N塞区间，以提升线路使用效率，这样的做法在日本十分常见。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:48.00,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}原则上一架信号机对应一个进路，当遇到有通往左侧或右侧或左右两侧都\N有侧线的咽喉时，侧向进路的信号机应列于正向进路信号机左或右的下方，\N以区分正向开通或侧向开通。当进路过多或空间不足等原因无法安装对应\N进路数量的信号机时可使用进路表示器来代替。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:53.92,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}注：「北斗星」号目前日本走行距离最长的定期旅客列车，全程1214.7公里；\N定期列车为札幌货物终点站-福冈货物终点站间经由日本海纵贯线、东海道\N·山阳本线的高速货第3071～2098/2070～3099～99列车，全程2127.7公里，\N历时约40小时。
